⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Frank Powell
node HRD · HRD · ⟦Frank Powell:HRD:dd6b0a⟧

WHO   — Frank Powell — the father who won't say it
WHAT  — The grail and the wound: the father-figure whose approval is the whole point, whose heart surgery becomes the absurd quest.
WHERE — HRD · Hot Rod (2007)  Framework inputs: Hot Rod (2007, dir. Akiva Schaffer, The Lonely Island/Paramount); verified cast & facts  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the parable needs a father who won't say he's proud — until, grudgingly, he must.
HOW   — By out-fighting Rod again and again, and by being the man Rod will heal in order to defeat in order to be loved by.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I'll respect you when you can beat me, kid. Funny thing — you spent everything you had keeping me alive long enough to try.

